<li><p>给定一个$n$维输入：<br><br>$\mathbf{X} = \left[x_{1}, x_{2}, \ldots, x_{n} \right]^{T}$</p>
</li>
<li><p>线性模型的权重参数和偏置：<br><br>$\mathbf{W} = \left[w_{1}, w_{2}, \dots, w_{n} \right]^{T}, \enspace b$</p>
</li>
<li><p>输出则是输入的加权和：<br><br>$\mathbf{y} = w_{1}x_{1} + w_{2}x_{2} + \dots, + w_{n}x_{n}  + b $</p>
</li>
</ul>
